  <summary date="2024-09-09T13:40:53Z" status="Introduced in House">Making Agricultural Products Locally Essential (MAPLE) Act

This bill includes maple syrup as one of the eligible&#160;foods under the&#160;Senior Farmers' Market Nutrition Program (SFMNP).&#160;

The Department of Agriculture's&#160;SFMNP provides grants to participating states to provide low-income seniors with coupons/vouchers that&#160;may be used at farmers&#226;&#8364;&#8482; markets, roadside stands, and community supported agriculture programs to purchase eligible foods (i.e., fresh, nutritious, locally-grown fruits, vegetables, herbs, and honey).</summary>
